{"type":null,"faqId":19945,"title":"如何开启或关闭重力感应？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>您可以通过如下两种方式开启或关闭重力感应：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>滑动状态栏，打开快捷操作面板。点击自动旋转图标即可快速开启或关闭重力感应。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"figd0e172\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=66651\" style=\"width:3.132639in;height:2.5743055in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n <span>在主屏幕上点击“设置 &gt; 辅助功能”，勾选或清除“自动旋转屏幕”复选框，也可开启或关闭重力感应功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"figd0e186\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=66652\" style=\"width:2.6791666in;height:3.9381945in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<a name=\"gen-id1.2.3.2.3\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=66653\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":166,"faqType":"显示与外观","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3366","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Screen-Display","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1425286521000,"seriesProductName":"T1-821w,T1-823L","visitedTimes":35,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"重力,重力感应,自动旋转,开启,关闭、旋转屏幕、自动","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}